name: cxxfilt
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "cxxfilt" %}
{% set version = "0.2.0" %}

package:
  name: "{{ name|lower }}"
  version: "{{ version }}"

source:
  url: "https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz"
  sha256: 6431205e2a2fe99cd7834e23e6a4224281e130a00f7cd2572e06d36cd208e801

build:
  number: 0
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv "
  skip: True  # [win]

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ compiler('c') }}
    - {{ compiler('cxx') }}
  host:
    - pip
    - python
  run:
    - python

test:
  imports:
    - cxxfilt

about:
  home: "https://github.com/afg984/python-cxxfilt"
  license: "BSD 2-Clause"
  license_family: "BSD"
  license_file: "LICENSE"
  summary: "Python interface to c++filt / abi::__cxa_demangle"
  doc_url: "https://pypi.org/project/cxxfilt/"
  dev_url: "https://github.com/afq984/python-cxxfilt"

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - oblute
    - benhuff
    - rluria14
